{"tid":2262542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴警闖西灣河教堂拘捕示威者 將一支鎚子塞進被告背包","createTime":"2020-10-29T07:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T15:16:17.000Z","uid":56115,"like":187,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a8c48b4aca25f8d5ac4d06c881d9d73c5737e5","tid":2262542,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"去年11.11交通警於西灣河槍擊學生，成安街亦有多人被捕。其中兩人被指戴口罩並攜有鎚子，被控參與非法集結，案件今於東區裁判法院開審。負責拘捕首被告的警員作供指，當日見首被告站在群眾最前線向警方指罵，具領導角色，認為對方已干犯非法集結罪。他當日曾追截被告至附近的聖十字架堂內，並在走廊內以警棍兩度擊打被告手腳，將其制服。辯方則質疑他拉錯人。<br />\n<br />\n據(黑警) 張指，此時首被告左邊腰間跌出一支木柄鎚子，他於是將之塞進首被告的背包。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問則指，當時現場人數眾多，並有走動，而且大部份衣著相同，張與他們亦有一定距離，難以辨認其後拘捕的首被告，就是最初的目標人物。張承認在首被告停留的成安街與大石街交界，有約50人聚集，他確未能全部「睇清楚」，惟首被告站在最前線，他一直有留意，當時首被告身邊未有相同衣著特徵的人士。下午續審。"},{"pid":"8013e6f5469fe84a58956d767818167de0bd4ab5","tid":2262542,"uid":56115,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/R3KWD7PEOVGAPH3DHRJHOCLLCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FR3KWD7PEOVGAPH3DHRJHOCLLCQ%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KijC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=37e1a630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FR3KWD7PEOVGAPH3DHRJHOCLLCQ%2F&h=1fc2e395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/R3KWD7PEOVGAPH3DHRJHOCLLCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"7e40265670ad3a772ca6f2ee09b5ae0108a69f9a","tid":2262542,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b34b628c6d22e6922ac09f0447fb4096a35494","tid":2262542,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd955b160